Odaily Planet Daily News: Binance co-founder He Yi said, "We believe that the interests of users and platforms are completely consistent. Binance can only continue to grow with the support of users. We will start from the following aspects:
Reduce industry rates as soon as possible;
Provide better services;
Establish industry compliance standards to ensure healthy development of the industry;
Our management team always stands at the forefront and puts user needs first. Currently, the Binance management team provides customer service at least once a quarter to handle ordinary user issues.
